name: BLACK ZONE
description:
Starting from self-anxiety about gripping conditions that result in
(image in prejudice) Image in refers to human attitudes towards humans
other. The condition when humans are afraid of humans and humans take over
the power of the universe, snatching destiny from what it should be. Crowd happens
in all corners of the world, is cultural socialism still being maintained? With various
kinds of problems in real life...everything has changed, as if they weren't mutually exclusive
do not believe. Is the universe still a friend to all humans? Or just priority
to the ruler? "Black Zone" is a description of space
anxiety and selfishness.
